  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1324597/" class="title-link">欲望的膨胀</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1324597"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2026015/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2026015-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2026015/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">求缺客</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-12"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-12 17:15:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1324597_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       德川家康重用的大贺弥四郎企图谋反。令家康很难堪。过早重用了他。   弥四郎把筑山夫人践踏在脚下，欲望不断膨胀,最终模糊了梦幻和现实之间的界限。      关注大人物时，请关注小人物！    第三部刚阅！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1324597/#comments">(1回应)</a>
