  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4961985/" class="title-link">德川家康的女人们~~~</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4961985"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/44055015/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u44055015-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/44055015/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">babyjj</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-05-24"
      class="main-meta">2011-05-24 16:49:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4961985_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看完三本德川家康，才发现每一部的名字都是独有深意的。可以说每一部都围绕着家康的命运而写。而每一部的名字也是随着家康命运的变化而定。崛起三河、天下布武......  同样身为女子，在看德川家康的时候，比起男子战场充满雄性味道的厮杀，我更喜欢看描写女子在后庭充满胭脂水...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4961985/#comments">(1回应)</a>
