        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34050267/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34050267/" class="">第35页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/68595974/" class=" " title="小错">小错</a>
                (Keep calm and carry on)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="34050267">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">白昼之枭，勇猛，可是却看不见任何东西。没有方向的时候会不会就是白昼之枭呢？</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-01-19 07:24</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                白昼之枭，勇猛，可是却看不见任何东西。没有方向的时候会不会就是白昼之枭呢？
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







